        5/19/2017
    








1 check-in
        


This is a review for the IdentoGO services provided inside this H&R Block.I came here to complete my TSA PreCheck application. The place was empty save for the one guy working here. All the empty cubicles made this place feel like an abandoned building in a ghost town. That's what happens when tax season is over!I had an appointment, but I could've easily have just walked in. After I signed in, the gentleman took me to the back of the office and seated me in front of a monitor. He went over my information (which was already in the system because I'd entered it when booking my appointment), took my fingerprints digitally (no messy ink!), and took my credit card for payment.The whole process was extremely efficient and was over in 5 minutes. Seriously, it took me longer to write this review than the amount of time I spent in the H&R Block office!




