        2/25/2012
    








First to Review
        


I am impressed!Obviously, I am writing this review about my own personal experience (a somewhat basic tax return) and everyone has different tax issues, but I can say that I was pleasantly surprised by the customer service and tax support at this H&R Block location. I have heard some horror stories about H&R Block and I was usure of what the process would be like. I made an appointment with William Lucas. I came in and was helped right away. William is obviously highly knowledgeable in tax preparation. He was SO helpful and answered all of my questions. He truly presented fantastic customer service. He encouraged me to do what was best for me and even encouraged me to file taxes on my own if possible, to avoid high fees on a basic return. I walked away feeling like he really cares about me and is not just after my money. You don't see too many people like that these days. I am sure that all tax preparers are different, but William appeared to be top notch and I would definitely recommend him. You can view the tax preparer profiles on the H&R Block website to see what kind of education and experience they have. Next time I have tax questions or need someone to do my taxes, I will head over to H&R Block without hesitation.




