H&R Block Tax Software Options

File simply and securely with tax software from Block.
With secure data technology for safe filing and free audit support, you can prepare your taxes with confidence. H&R Block tax software also offers up to five free federal e‑files.
 









Tax Identity Theft is Growing

The IRS estimates that tax identity theft resulted in more than $2 billion in stolen refunds from taxes filed in 2016. You can help better protect yourself from this serious threat with our exclusive prevention and restoration services provided by Tax Identity Care protection and restoration services. It’s available with any software product at checkout.










