The Software Filing Experience
Block tax preparation software allows you to chat with a tax expert for free unlimited advice. Importing your W2 and 1099 information from last year’s return is also free. Before you file, our software double-checks your return for any potential issues so that you have the best tax software experience possible. And like all Block products and services, we are committed to monitoring and protecting your data 24/7.


